definitions.text:
@sá quản
- Not mind
=Sá quản đường xa+Not to mind the distance

@sá gì
- not matter
=sá gì ba cái chuyện cỏn con ấy+it doesn't matter such trivial things

@sá bao
- not much
=sá bao tiền+not much money

@sá kể
- irrespective of, regardless of
=sá kể sang hèn+regardless of social status
